<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">

<title>Special Delivery ❤️</title>

<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@300;500&family=Dancing+Script:wght@600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

<style>

body{
margin:0;
font-family:'Poppins',sans-serif;
height:100vh;
display:flex;
justify-content:center;
align-items:center;
background:linear-gradient(135deg,#ffd6e7,#ffeef6);
overflow:hidden;
text-align:center;
}

.container{
width:320px;
}

.badge{
background:white;
color:#ff4fa3;
font-size:12px;
padding:6px 12px;
border-radius:20px;
display:inline-block;
margin-bottom:10px;
letter-spacing:1px;
}

h1{
color:#ff2e8a;
font-size:22px;
margin:10px 0;
}

.subtitle{
font-size:12px;
color:#777;
margin-bottom:20px;
}

.envelope{
width:300px;
height:180px;
background:#ffd1e6;
border-radius:10px;
position:relative;
cursor:pointer;
box-shadow:0 10px 25px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
overflow:hidden;
}

.flap{
position:absolute;
width:100%;
height:100%;
background:#ffc0dd;
clip-path:polygon(0 0,100% 0,50% 60%);
transition:0.6s;
transform-origin:top;
}

.envelope.open .flap{
transform:rotateX(180deg);
}

.letter{
position:absolute;
background:white;
width:85%;
height:120px;
left:7.5%;
bottom:10px;
border-radius:8px;
padding:15px;
box-sizing:border-box;
font-size:14px;
transform:translateY(80px);
transition:0.6s;
}

.envelope.open .letter{
transform:translateY(-20px);
}

.letter p{
opacity:0;
transition:0.6s;
}

.envelope.open .letter p{
opacity:1;
}

.hello{
position:absolute;
right:-5px;
bottom:-5px;
width:60px;
}

.footer{
margin-top:15px;
font-size:11px;
color:#ff4fa3;
}

</style>
</head>

<body>

<div class="container">

<div class="badge">SPECIAL DELIVERY</div>

<h1>Happy Women's Day, My Love!</h1>

<div class="subtitle">
Something from the heart, just for you 💌
</div>

<div class="envelope" onclick="openLetter()" id="envelope">

<div class="flap"></div>

<div class="letter">
<p>
You are strong, beautiful, and amazing.  
Today is about celebrating the incredible woman you are.  
Thank you for bringing happiness into my life.  

Happy Women's Day ❤️
</p>
</div>

<img class="hello" src="https://i.imgur.com/8QfQYQK.png">

</div>

<div class="footer">
Opening with love...
</div>

</div>

<script>

function openLetter(){
document.getElementById("envelope").classList.toggle("open");
}

</script>

</body>
</html>